OL,3,CLord Mandelson no longer on bail as
OL,4,Che's released under investigation by
OL,5,Cpolice
OL,7,FLord Peter Mandelson is no longer on
OL,8,Fpolice bail, and has instead been
OL,9,Freleased under investigation after his
OL,10,Farrest last Monday on suspicion of
OL,11,Fmisconduct in public office.
OL,13,FA Metropolitan Police spokesperson
OL,14,Fsaid: "A 72-year-old man arrested on
OL,15,Fsuspicion of misconduct in public
OL,16,Foffice has been released under
OL,17,Finvestigation.
OL,19,F"The investigation remains ongoing".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
