OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772838680
OL,3,CLord Mandelson no longer on bail as
OL,4,Che's released under investigation by
OL,5,Cpolice
OL,7,FPolice officers had arrested Mandelson
OL,8,Flast Monday after reports the former
OL,9,FUS Ambassador was a flight risk, a
OL,10,Fclaim his lawyers have denied.
OL,12,FMandelson spent around nine hours in
OL,13,Fpolice custody before he was released
OL,14,Fon bail, a condition that meant he
OL,15,Fwould have had his passport taken away.
OL,17,FThe fact he is now under investigation
OL,18,Frather than on bail suggests is no
OL,19,Flonger considered a flight risk, and
OL,20,Fwill have his passport returned.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
