CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772838680
OL,3,CLord Mandelson no longer on bail as
OL,4,Che's released under investigation by
OL,5,Cpolice
OL,7,FIn a statement in Parliament last
OL,8,FWednesday morning, Sir Lindsay said he
OL,9,Fwanted to confirm media reports that
OL,10,Fhe was the source of the information,
OL,11,Fwhich Lord Mandelson claims was the
OL,12,Freason for his arrest, to "prevent any
OL,13,Finaccurate speculation".
OL,15,FHoyle had reportedly been informed
OL,16,Fthat the peer was allegedly planning
OL,17,Fto flee Britain for the British Virgin
OL,18,FIslands.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
