OL,3,CLord Mandelson no longer on bail as
OL,4,Che's released under investigation by
OL,5,Cpolice
OL,7,FLawyers working for Mandelson said
OL,8,Flast Tuesday that his arrest was
OL,9,F"prompted by a baseless suggestion
OL,10,Fthat he was planning to leave the
OL,11,Fcountry and take up permanent
OL,12,Fresidence abroad".
OL,14,F"There is absolutely no truth
OL,15,Fwhatsoever in any such suggestion. We
OL,16,Fhave asked the MPS for the evidence
OL,17,Frelied upon to justify the arrest,"
OL,18,Fthey said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
